{{Top|leg}}
The '''ion double blaster''' was a form of [[Ion blaster/Legends|ion weapon]] used by the [[B1-series battle droid/Legends|B1-series battle droid]] owned by [[Wittin/Legends|Wittin]] during [[Jabba Desilijic Tiure/Legends|Jabba]] the [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt's]] demolition contest. When charged up, it had the capacity to disable anything from a [[Rancor/Legends|rancor]] to a [[T-47 airspeeder/Legends|T-47 snowspeeder]] in a single shot, but would have to be charged up again after every shot.

